(337,14990,'19. A. Bartoloni et al. A Hardware Implementation of the APE100 Architecture. In-ternational J. of Modern Phsysics, C(4):969, 1993.The architecture which has been chosen by B¨orger for Del Castillo?s Tesi di Laureato try out ASMs for modeling real-world architectures, in the context of reengi-neering project for this machine which had been launched by a group of physicistsin Pisa and Rome, see [71],[70].',0,0),
