(337,15026,'53. E. B¨orger. Why Use Evolving Algebras for Hardware and Software Engineer-ing? In M. Bartosek, J. Staudek, and J. Wiederman, editors, Proceedings of SOF-SEM?95, 22nd Seminar on Current Trends in Theory and Practice of Informatics,volume 1012 of LNCS, pages 236?271. Springer, 1995.A presentation of the salient features of ASMs, as part of a discussion and surveyof the use of ASMs in design and analysis of hardware and software systems. Theleading example is detailed and improved in [88].',0,0),
