(337,15152,'174. Y. Gurevich. Reconsidering Turing?s Thesis: Toward More Realistic Semanticsof Programs. Technical Report CRL-TR-38-84, EECS Department, University ofMichigan, 1984.An attempt to reconsider Turing?s Thesis, taking into account that resources arebounded. The earliest known paper in which the ideas behind ASMs began totake form. See the continuation in [175].',0,0),
