(337,15159,'181. Y. Gurevich. Evolving Algebras 1993: Lipari Guide. In E. B¨orger, editor, Speci-?cation and Validation Methods, pages 9?36. Oxford University Press, 1995.The notion of sequential ASMs de?ned in [179] is extended to cover distributedcomputations. A later update May 1997 Draft of the ASM Guide appeared asTechnical Report CSE-TR-336-97, EECS Dept., University of Michigan.',0,0),
