(337,15171,'193. Y. Gurevich, N. Soparkar, and C. Wallace. Formalizing Database Recovery.Journal of Universal Computer Science, 3(4):320?340, 1997.A database recovery algorithm (the undo-redo algorithm) is modeled at severallevels of abstraction, with veri?cation of the correctness of the high-level modeland of each of the four re?nement steps. An updated version of the TechnicalReports CSE-TR-249-95 and CSE-TR-327-97 of EECS Department, Universityof Michigan, Ann Arbor, and of the paper Formalizing Recovery in Transaction-Oriented Database Systems of C. Wallace and Y. Gurevich and N. Soparkar,published in S. Chaudhuri and A. Deshpande and R. Krishnamurthy (Eds.): Pro-ceedings of the Seventh International Conference on Management of Data, TataMcGraw-Hill, New Delhi, India, 1995, pages 166-185.',1,1),
