(337,15259,'277. J. Schmid. Executing ASM Speci?cations with AsmGofer. Web pageshttp://www.tydo.de/AsmGofer.The Web site for the machine to execute, equipped with graphical user interface,ASMs which are enhanced with the structuring and composition concepts de?nedin [103]. AsmGofer executes all the ASMs de?ned in [291]. In [116] AsmGofer hasbeen used to build a simulator for UML state diagrams.',0,0),
