(337,15289,'304. C. Wallace. The Semantics of the Java Programming Language: PreliminaryVersion. Technical Report CSE-TR-355-97, EECS Dept., University of Michigan,December 1997.A speci?cation of the static and dynamic semantics of Java, using ASMs andMontages. This work showed the shortcomings of the original formulation of Mon-tages [224] and led to its state machine based reformulation in [11]. See [223]and the independent earlier Java modeling work [106] which was continued in',0,0),
